      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古橋　綾菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN002B_023",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan002B_023.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「ああっ……お願い、もっと強くっ……！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV014・目閉じ・脱いでる・愛液",
        "file": "EV014_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "覗いているという罪悪感と、その背徳的な興奮に、",
